{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Prevent family courts and social services making decisions based on hearsay",
        "additional_details": "This can have dreadful results leading to torment and psychological effect on children and parents.\r\n \r\nChildren should only ever be removed from a family if there is unambiguous evidence of harm. It is fundamentally cruel what is happening here in the UK and change is long overdue.\r\n \r\nIt can happen to someone in any family.",
        "background": "At present social services and courts can take decisions about family matters based on hearsay, which is not normally admissible as evidence. This means that families can be torn apart based solely on hearsay.",
